data.description: *Price Improvement* Interested Buyers & Agents, seller contributing up to 2% towards Buyers fees or Closing Cost. Welcome to Riverstone in Alamo Ranch San Antonio Texas. Step inside this gorgeous 3,401 SQFT home with both elegance and comfort. Culberson Mill is full of exterior and interior upgrades. Those of which include 4 sided brick, 3 car garage and almost a .25 acre size lot. Cathedral style 20 foot ceilings with grand staircase, double ovens, 5 burner gas stove, oak cabinets, large stone fireplace and generous size closets in all bedrooms. Home has full irrigation system along with a large back patio with an above ground pool (new pump installed 2023) and natural gas line in back for grill.  All carpets professionally steam cleaned and freshly vacuumed. Minutes from Fiesta Texas and Sea world. Home to top rated schools and near by several shops, dinning and movies. Schedule your showing today.
